                  HOW TO
                  Ingredients
                  WHAT IT IS

                  Longwearing innovative ultra-matte lipstick with the staying power of a stain and the intense color of a liquid lipstick.

                  TELL ME MORE
                  • 8 hour longwear formula
                  • Infused with Volulip for a no-sting plumping &smoothing effect
                  • Features Avocado Oil, Vitamin E & Hyaluronic Filling
                    • Spheres to moisturize & smooth lips
                  • Comfortable, lightweight formula
                  • Angled applicator for precise application
                  OUR INSPIRATION

                  Lipstick is never more beautiful, pigmented, and rich than in its melted form in the cosmetic lab. We took our iconic Melted formula and created a matte version infused with a no-sting plumping filler, creating a smooth canvas for rich matte color that never appears dry.

                  Use applicator tip to outline lips, then use the flat edge to fill in color.

                  Isododecane, Cyclopentasiloxane, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Dimethicone, Kaolin, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Silica Dimethyl Silylate, Hydrogenated Polyisobutene, Beeswax\Cera Alba\Cire D'abeille, Propylene Carbonate, Cyclohexasiloxane, Tocopheryl Acetate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Retinyl Palmitate, Portulaca Pilosa Extract, Glyceryl Behenate/Eicosadioate, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Cetearyl Ethylhexanoate, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Sucrose Cocoate, Palmitoyl Tripeptide-38, Hydrogen Dimethicone, Sorbitan Isostearate, Butylene Glycol, Pentylene Glycol, Tocopherol, [+/- Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491), Iron Oxides (CI 77492), Iron Oxides (CI 77499), Red 7 Lake (CI 15850), Red 28 Lake (CI 45410), Red 30 Lake (CI 73360), Yellow 5 Lake (CI 19140), Blue 1 Lake (CI 42090), Red 7 (CI 15850), Orange 5 (CI 45370), Bronze Powder (CI 77400), RED 27 (CI 45410), Copper Powder (CI 77400), Red 6 (CI 15850), Yellow 6 Lake (CI 15985), RED 21 (CI 45380), Red 33 Lake (CI 17200), Bismuth Oxychloride (CI 77163), Manganese Violet (CI 77742), Red 22 Lake (CI 45380)]

                  Please be aware that ingredient lists may change or vary from time to time. Please refer to the ingredient list on the product package you receive for the most up to date list of ingredients.
